Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.64,0:00:21.40,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找尋著看不見的明天 著急地用手觸摸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.56,0:00:25.91,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而受傷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.10,0:00:38.50,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來是沒有出口的迷宮 就像需要解謎的拼圖一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.16,0:00:49.77,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使沒有奇跡出現   夢想也將成為勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.01,0:00:54.94,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feel your Heart  在荏苒的季節中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.09,0:00:57.86,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你的憧憬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.01,0:01:00.36,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just my Love  因為那份思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.51,0:01:03.65,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我了無形的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.93,0:01:09.77,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像稍微感受到了迷惘和煩惱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.77,0:01:11.29,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論在什麼時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.44,0:01:14.66,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feel your Heart  在荏苒的季節中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.45,0:01:23.59,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just my Love  對你的思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.62,0:01:28.59,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feel your Heart
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.56,0:21:22.83,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love is burning 在心中綻放的玫瑰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.94,0:21:29.63,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在黑暗中燃盡  僅是一束火焰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.91,0:21:38.30,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在滿是隔閡的街上 如遊戲般的迷失自我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.45,0:21:42.56,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以小丑的心情躊躇著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.43,0:21:50.90,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要踐踏悲傷的殘片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.05,0:21:55.28,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人在未來中戀愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.81,0:22:03.37,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以解開今晚的謎底仍然是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.64,0:22:07.88,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up！真面目  Hurry up！回到從前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.20,0:22:15.42,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love is passion　兩個人的手中充滿的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.58,0:22:22.39,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投入黑暗之中  想緊緊擁抱住陽光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.83,0:22:27.94,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love is burning 在迷宮中相互Kiss
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.06,0:22:36.99,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁向樂園  僅差一道門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.65,0:00:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨著時代的演進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.32,0:00:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,困難的案件也與日俱增
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.86,0:00:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的故事是尋寶之旅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.74,0:00:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否能尋找到心靈之寶呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.61,0:00:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.24,0:00:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.15,0:00:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.24,0:00:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.24,0:01:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偵探團探險生存事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.09,0:01:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來在這裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.02,0:02:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士 這是真的地圖嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.73,0:02:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 當然是真的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.89,0:02:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.19,0:02:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界上真的有寶物囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.61,0:02:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個要等你們到了以後才知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.32,0:02:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會找到寶物的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.91,0:02:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會找到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.20,0:02:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.70,0:02:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士 我問你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.49,0:02:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那張奇怪的東西到底從哪來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.37,0:02:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.00,0:02:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你也不會說實話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.71,0:02:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 你只要到了終點就知道怎麼回事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.46,0:02:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終點啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.86,0:02:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大不小了還尋什麼寶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.90,0:02:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 大家現在所在的位置就是白骨之木了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.95,0:02:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個就先以倫敦木橋為目標出發吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.24,0:03:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我就在這裏慢慢地釣魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.83,0:03:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你們這趟探險愉快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.58,0:03:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.46,0:03:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是小孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.92,0:03:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前是小孩子嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.80,0:03:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.80,0:03:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想寶物是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.68,0:03:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶物是什麼 這我們哪會知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.22,0:03:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.81,0:03:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是很值錢的寶物才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.85,0:03:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不對 光彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.43,0:03:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 不是鑽石就是寶石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.98,0:03:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定是德川時代藏的金子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.48,0:03:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 那也不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.44,0:03:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.46,0:03:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看地圖上倫敦木橋這個名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.54,0:03:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為它會掉下去 害我擔心得要命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.05,0:03:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是在電影裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.11,0:03:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的爛橋我們一定會掉下去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.27,0:04:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.48,0:04:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真不能開玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.40,0:04:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士那個傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.94,0:04:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然讓我們到這麼危險的地方來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.74,0:04:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下子要怎麼回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.08,0:04:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指南針在這個地方根本就不管用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.00,0:04:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個傢伙到底為什麼要把寶物藏在這種山裡面呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.21,0:04:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想那個傢伙一定是個很有神秘感的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.30,0:04:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也未免太神秘過頭了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.89,0:04:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.93,0:04:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地圖上有五顆杉木 這裡只有四棵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.14,0:04:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是這裡沒有錯嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.10,0:04:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實那個傢伙也真倒楣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.10,0:04:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼看著就可以找到這些寶物的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.69,0:04:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他卻因為事故死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.90,0:04:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這一次可是出來尋寶的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.28,0:05:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你說話你也答個腔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.61,0:05:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣很危險 叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.37,0:05:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們要把香煙的火熄了才能夠丟掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.16,0:05:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是引起森林大火的話那就糟糕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.45,0:05:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是幹什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.37,0:05:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們四個是少年偵探團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.05,0:05:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那張地圖跟我們的好像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.26,0:05:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在看什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.22,0:05:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.76,0:05:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.60,0:05:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走？ 要到什麼地方去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.80,0:05:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.31,0:05:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個人絕對不可能是來爬山的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.31,0:05:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不但帶著鐵鏟 還穿著西裝和皮鞋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.73,0:05:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外那張地圖到底是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.36,0:05:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在在這個地方對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.33,0:05:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想應該沒錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.29,0:05:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜指南針點忙都幫不上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.16,0:05:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 這裡只有四棵杉木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.37,0:05:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是這裡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.67,0:05:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 就是這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.13,0:05:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個讓開一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.13,0:06:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看 這就是第五棵杉木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.18,0:06:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它只是被砍掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.38,0:06:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以有一點難以辨認而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.51,0:06:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看看這顆樹的年輪很稀疏吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.81,0:06:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個就是太陽非常充裕的部份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.64,0:06:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以這樣子樹的成長也會比較好一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.31,0:06:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說 南方在那邊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.27,0:06:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全正確
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.23,0:06:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們要走哪條路好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.19,0:06:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地圖給我看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.99,0:06:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"惡魔之手"要從"狹窄的門"進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.49,0:06:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡魔之手就是指左手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.62,0:06:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以應該是左邊的兩條路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.70,0:06:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是它又說要從狹窄的門進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.75,0:06:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們只要走比較窄的路就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.12,0:06:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南什麼都知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.50,0:06:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來惡魔之手就是左手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.38,0:06:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那右手是什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.92,0:06:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是天使之手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.18,0:06:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼單純嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.31,0:06:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那幾個小孩子怎麼會有那張地圖呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.93,0:06:56.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幾個小孩子的腦袋還真不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.85,0:06:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我們不能讓他們先到 快走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.91,0:07:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那兩個人好像有點怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.58,0:07:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們一定也是來找我們的寶物的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.25,0:07:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們剛才的確有提到寶物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.25,0:07:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定錯不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.60,0:07:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命…我要沉下去了…救命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.73,0:07:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…我要淹死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.86,0:07:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…光彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.53,0:07:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起來看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.12,0:07:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 我還以為我死定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.55,0:08:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種火柴不管風吹得多大都可以點著的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.97,0:08:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是現在濕了也沒用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.55,0:08:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.30,0:08:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還在想說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.26,0:08:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把火升起來了就可以把濕的衣服烤乾的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.85,0:08:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.98,0:08:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把手電筒的頭部拆掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.56,0:08:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把裡面的反射板拿下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.15,0:08:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再將火柴放進反射板裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.15,0:08:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後把這個正對著太陽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.86,0:08:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓它的光線集中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.11,0:08:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種火柴就算再好 濕了還是不能用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.45,0:08:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣弄還是點不著吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.42,0:08:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.01,0:08:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好棒喔 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.26,0:08:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.88,0:08:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像是老奶奶的智囊袋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.80,0:08:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這叫求生技能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.27,0:09:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 到底要走哪條路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.53,0:09:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.36,0:09:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面好像寫了什麼東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.61,0:09:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是寫的不太清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.45,0:09:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是"東"的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.12,0:09:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這個"東"到底指的是哪一邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.25,0:09:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.72,0:09:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓那幾個孩子去是不是太危險了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.18,0:09:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火滅掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.81,0:09:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滅火確認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.27,0:09:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們真的可以直走到最後一關嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.19,0:09:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那個斜坡在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.81,0:09:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想再爬那個斜坡上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.36,0:09:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放心好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.07,0:09:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在在這個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.61,0:09:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能從這邊這條彎曲的小路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.28,0:09:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以到下一個目的地了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.07,0:09:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們現在出發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.15,0:11:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.85,0:11:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鈞一髮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.24,0:11:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被折斷的地方還很新
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.25,0:11:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個痕跡一定是被什麼銳利的東西砍斷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.79,0:11:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過絕對不是刀子或刀劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.79,0:11:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而是鐵鏟之類的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.34,0:11:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鐵鏟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.51,0:11:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.80,0:11:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個人到這兒來過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.10,0:11:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面到底寫了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.43,0:11:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這上面好像是什麼暗號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.56,0:11:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是看不清楚怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.73,0:11:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.98,0:11:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰上這種情況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.27,0:11:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把紙放到上面用鉛筆塗一塗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.73,0:11:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面的字不就會浮現出來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.40,0:11:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.95,0:12:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我這次出來沒有帶鉛筆跟紙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.12,0:12:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帶了奇異筆不知道可不可以用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.91,0:12:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這倒可以試試看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.16,0:12:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這個？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.25,0:12:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.79,0:12:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是說用步美說的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.04,0:12:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.59,0:12:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.46,0:12:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.05,0:12:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先把水壺的水倒到這塊板子上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.72,0:12:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再將有字的部份塗上一點土
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.10,0:12:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再將多餘的去掉之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.06,0:12:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.73,0:12:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凹槽裡面有了土
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.10,0:12:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就知道是什麼暗號了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.94,0:12:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝著時鐘上的太陽指針所指示的東方前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.40,0:12:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東方在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.61,0:12:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.66,0:12:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一次沒有年輪可以看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.24,0:12:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽指針…朝東方前進…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.29,0:12:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.66,0:12:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.46,0:12:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子應該就可以解決方向的謎題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.05,0:12:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把時針指向太陽的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.92,0:13:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時針和十二點之間二分之一的方向就是南方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.18,0:13:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說東方就是在它左邊的九十度角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.51,0:13:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.22,0:13:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊就是東方了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.64,0:13:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.19,0:13:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老奶奶的智囊袋二度立大功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.48,0:13:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.86,0:13:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.98,0:13:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從天之水與天之石的交界開始走五步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.48,0:13:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天之水指的是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.82,0:13:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是雨水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.03,0:13:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個答案也未免太單純了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.78,0:14:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.95,0:14:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有五根石柱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.41,0:14:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣看起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.95,0:14:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元太 肩膀借我一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.66,0:14:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼 幹嘛爬上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.42,0:14:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石柱的排列剛好是W形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.91,0:14:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,W
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.71,0:14:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,WEST
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.59,0:14:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 是西方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.22,0:14:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣說起來的話天之水又是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.13,0:14:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 你想通了沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.30,0:14:29.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是從石柱往西走五步吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.40,0:14:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 什麼都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.32,0:14:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.20,0:14:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過不是W就是M
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.37,0:14:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者也可以把它想成是B
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.58,0:14:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天之水是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.79,0:14:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.25,0:14:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 光彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.62,0:14:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光彥 你在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.50,0:14:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.96,0:14:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.96,0:14:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.50,0:14:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被一棵樹絆倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.17,0:15:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒下以後頭又撞到那邊的石頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.47,0:15:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樹跟石頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.43,0:15:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些石頭看起來很久沒有動過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.14,0:15:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.65,0:15:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個形狀難道是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.11,0:15:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圓木跟石頭連成了北斗七星的形狀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.62,0:15:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.87,0:15:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大熊星座就是勺的形狀 也就是天之水了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.70,0:15:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.92,0:15:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.13,0:15:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些石柱就是仙后星座
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.34,0:15:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.05,0:15:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天之水和天之石的交點指的就是北極星了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.59,0:15:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而北極星的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.18,0:15:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是北斗七星頂端兩顆星的距離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.93,0:15:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,延長了五倍之後的距離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.23,0:15:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外仙后星座的W型的兩端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.85,0:16:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,則是從兩側星星延伸的交點開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.32,0:16:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連接中央的星延長五倍之後的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.12,0:16:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 博士這個人心眼還真壞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.37,0:16:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有個石頭上面也有寫東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.50,0:16:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是那個沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.04,0:16:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北極星是P0L0RIS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.59,0:16:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開頭的英文字母是P
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.42,0:16:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.51,0:16:26.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定就是這個地方沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.01,0:16:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.76,0:16:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只要走五步就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.06,0:16:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一、二、三、四、五
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.19,0:16:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快跳開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.90,0:16:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 我們走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.66,0:16:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 這個是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.33,0:17:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一定就是寶物了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.54,0:17:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點打開來看一看 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.80,0:17:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說這些寶物是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.93,0:17:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 光彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.43,0:17:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就可以吃光全世界的鰻魚飯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.89,0:17:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 那我也要…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.77,0:17:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 這個時候潑你們冷水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.36,0:17:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點把那袋東西拿過來給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.78,0:17:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是剛才那個叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.61,0:17:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.82,0:17:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩個是珠寶大盜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.91,0:17:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點把那些東西交出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.08,0:17:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.00,0:17:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 這樣做是沒用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.84,0:17:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面那個叔叔要我把這個給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.93,0:17:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.31,0:18:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 你把他怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.44,0:18:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他被石頭絆倒 自己結果撞到頭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.57,0:18:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像光彥一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.16,0:18:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這有什麼好笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.57,0:18:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才撞到真的很痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.16,0:18:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.21,0:18:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是我們真正的寶物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.80,0:18:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說這個就是我們要找的寶物 是不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.30,0:18:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是一張紙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.60,0:18:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 那上面寫些什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.72,0:18:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的寶物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.23,0:18:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你們到達這個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.64,0:18:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,途中所經歷的一切過程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.27,0:18:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也許會從橋上掉進河裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.98,0:18:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要自己生火 自己抓魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.44,0:18:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不時需要朋友的幫助 才能夠克服重重的阻礙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.36,0:18:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些是寶貴的經驗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.41,0:19:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們現在也許還不能夠體會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.91,0:19:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我想將來總有一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.91,0:19:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切都會變成你們的無價之寶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.79,0:19:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為你們永遠的財產
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.29,0:19:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你們能夠將這個經驗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.38,0:19:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續地傳達給以後的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.63,0:19:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像沒有聽懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.60,0:19:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.97,0:19:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.40,0:19:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yusaku Kudoh (工藤優作)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.37,0:19:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到終點就知道怎麼回事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.20,0:19:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來這封信是爸爸寫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.75,0:19:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫K的時候在尾巴往上翹是他的習慣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.42,0:19:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說過這是誰都學不來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.17,0:19:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實一開始我就注意到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.72,0:20:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在紮營河岸對面這座山的山頂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.97,0:20:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我們這一次最終是標的藏寶地點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.10,0:20:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那棵樹上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.48,0:20:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子就可以看到阿笠博士的帳篷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.90,0:20:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這段距離雖然不怎麼長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.53,0:20:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是內容的確是非常充實的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.12,0:20:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽了我們的描述之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.66,0:20:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿笠博士立刻通知警方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.50,0:20:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這座山上來逮捕珠寶大盜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.87,0:20:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而因為製作我們的筆錄是在隔天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.63,0:20:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以到了隔天我們才可以回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.97,0:20:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始我根本不把這次尋寶放在眼裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.05,0:20:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這種冒險不管來幾次都不嫌膩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.06,0:20:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我今年已經十七歲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.89,0:20:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是為此雀躍不已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.36,0:20:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞了半天那些寶石雖然不是寶貝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.99,0:20:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是找到了 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.16,0:21:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確有寶藏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.45,0:21:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的寶藏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.45,0:21:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(工藤新一)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.34,0:22:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候正好是你出生後不久的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.39,0:22:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你爸爸本來準備發表的一份稿子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.06,0:22:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻被別人給偷走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.31,0:22:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被偷走了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.44,0:22:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們根據當時的情況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.94,0:22:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然把你爸爸那個偵探迷小偷的下落給找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.02,0:23:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是搞了半天那個小偷也找不到稿子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.07,0:23:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人就是那個死於意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.07,0:23:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把地圖畫下來的另外一個寶石強盜嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.78,0:23:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.58,0:23:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他不能夠發表偷來的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.79,0:23:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會到現在還沒有發表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.54,0:23:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到會用這種方式出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.72,0:23:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(給我的兒子 新一)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.49,0:23:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 小蘭他們不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.75,0:23:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭 危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.17,0:24:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭 快起來 快起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.18,0:24:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…為什麼要殺小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.22,0:24:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nxet Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.51,0:24:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山莊繃帶怪人殺人事件(前篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.56,0:24:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.85,0:24:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窺視孔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.27,0:24:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回是讓大家久等的前後篇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.40,0:24:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要在前篇把犯人找出來 嗯哼哼
